  {
    "title": "Lore",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "[“]Valir, my beloved brother."
          },
          {
            "text": "You lost everything the day we made The pact."
          },
          {
            "text": "I'll see to it that the Fire Kingdom restores everything to the way it once was."
          },
          {
            "text": "Even if you still wish to avenge your cruel father, I do not blame you as long as you can cast away the storm within your heart."
          },
          {
            "text": "Nothing is as important as your happiness, not even my life.[”] Vale fell into deep contemplation as he wrote his letter to Valir."
          },
          {
            "text": "Those first few lines brought Vale back to the days of his youth, when he and Valir were the closest of friends."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "As Vale fell further into nostalgia, he remembered the day they met at a royal party."
          },
          {
            "text": "Ever since then, they both felt a strong affinity towards each other's magic."
          },
          {
            "text": "For a long time, Vale and Valir were inseparable."
          },
          {
            "text": "Together they left many memories in the Valley of the Winds, the Fire Kingdom and many other exotic lands."
          },
          {
            "text": "When unrest flooded the Fire Kingdom, Valir quickly made his leave."
          },
          {
            "text": "Only Vale knows exactly how much Valir sacrificed that day."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "As time went on, the day of The pact was coming soon."
          },
          {
            "text": "Vale's magical abilities to control winds had grown more sophisticated over the years."
          },
          {
            "text": "In fact, he was the only member of his family who could change the winds with magic."
          },
          {
            "text": "Yet, Vale had never shown his magic to anyone before."
          },
          {
            "text": "Vale waited and waited for the day of The pact to come."
          },
          {
            "text": "On that day, he would put on a spectacular display of wind magic for Valir."
          },
          {
            "text": "Vale believes that Valir will see his magic, remember the precious times they had together, and return how things were in their youth."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "templates": [
      {
        "template": "clr"
      }
    ]
